display_long_description:
# Welcome to The ChicKing Dead! 🐔🧟‍♂️

Dive into a dystopian chicken world like no other, where creativity and chaos collide. As a heroic chicken, you must face a zombie virus outbreak while unraveling the sinister plans of a giant corporation. Survival isn't just about fighting—it's about strategy, skill, and a dash of absurd fun.
[media]

**Fly around. Like a chicken!**

You are a chicken. In a chaotic world full of zombies, spread your wings and escape!

[media]

**Turned into a zombie? Infect the other survivors!**

Slash survivors with the deadly claws on your wings and spread the infection! 
Wait, was that chicken your friend who was running away together? Well, this chaotic world, it’s none of my business!


[media]

**Master the Ultimate Chase!**

This isn’t just about running—it’s about breaking free! Glide, dash, boost, and chain your moves to take control of the chaos and leave your opponents in the dust!


[media]

**Level Up and Collect Free Coins and Feathers!** 

Whether you’re running for your life or infecting others, your efforts pay off. 
Level up and collect rewards—no matter if you’re a chicken or a zombie!


[media]

**Show Off Your Style as the Coolest Chicken!**

No matter how hectic it gets, fashion comes first! Discover a variety of costumes waiting for you. 
Show off your style and survive in the most fabulous way possible!
